-- Russian Urges Guinea to End Alleged Seizure of Rusal Unit
-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 2012-04-10T19:02:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-10/russian-urges-guinea-to-end-alleged-seizure-of-rusal-unit.html
Russia’s Foreign Ministry urged the
authorities in  Guinea  to “curb the illegal activities of trade
unions and radical elements” who it says took control of United
Co. Rusal’s Friguia bauxite and alumina complex, according to a
statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Jordan in Moscow at 
